{"tid":1454101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試著說*香港人，反抗*，不要說*香港人，加油*","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:32:30.000Z","uid":81236,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89a8210c90f8663c0031c58c5a3e92f9e0f3d4ab","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"唔好再講咩加油<br />\n<br />\n係要大家出黎反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee9bfa7c03841ca793966e07bfdf9b26b9abcad","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:12:50.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"c59ca74f517d1f824743f8a7cac4eb3c20a5d887","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:14:25.000Z","msg":"加油已經唔足夠"},{"pid":"5804b41988dfbadc0d980c8936edc4fb307b1519","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"b637c61d4fea86099665fa3b3092647bee23e6eb","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"以後遊行口號唔好再叫香港加油"},{"pid":"41c36c937187821e2bb15c3226669ecae8e45298","tid":1454101,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"[替天行道]你奪去我們的光明，我們送你入無盡的黑暗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1454138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1454138</a>"},{"pid":"79f22bccee46b9c1907ae4eaa457541ae13ff274","tid":1454101,"uid":104489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"叫香港人 起義 會唔會上口同響亮d呢"},{"pid":"b8e8ef23106754ffc62d7e0b355f52d35abc0775","tid":1454101,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"為自己及家人健康著想<br />\n請大家加緊對外用中英宣傳：香港鐵路系統已嚴重受<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有毒&amp;致癌吸入物污染</span></span></strong>，請避免乘搭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkObe5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkObe5e.jpg&h=fbcd3d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個同721 個point一樣<br />\n個個人都會避免搭港鐵<br />\n外國遊客聽到會驚<br />\n大陸人聽到更驚<br />\n當遊客自動唔黎=和塞機場異曲同工<br />\n打工仔改搭其他交通工具=造成大規模交通擠塞=影響番工=和罷工差不多<br />\n兩者直接造成香港經濟損失<br />\n<br />\nPush<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5236d9bf5009e2878d20b3a9b211c742c0dea3f6","tid":1454101,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b5f6f02778e02122d49753da44a96b6b1654a168","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:48:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ade8e1cdaf256ba0fb3784b60d83fb80669dd33","tid":1454101,"uid":102529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"59843d62048c4b3d9107b3bbcd832e4926f5ff2d","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"a859932afac226d3bbef8dd3c3093c1ab64e4ecb","tid":1454101,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:55:05.000Z","msg":"香港人腦海中唔好再只有加油<br />\n<br />\n讀書可以加油<br />\n考試可以加油<br />\n工作可以加油<br />\n<br />\n唯獨香港人唔可以只有加油"},{"pid":"ce16a3e2c3f0bbc2ca8bf9d7357d17779d31bbb2","tid":1454101,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"時機？一米開槍就一觸即發！<br />\n已經有好充分理由無限罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果你今日返緊工，一定好唔安樂。</strong></span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>放工入機場，聽日情緒病，後日要復診，全民持續告假！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n主動奪回自主權